original_title: Manhattan: Fort Charles Place - Jacobus Place
text:
Fort Charles Place, north from Jacobus Place to Marble Hill Avenue, showing the repaving of this thoroughfare by the Works Progress Administration. This series of photos is progressive.

May 3, 1937
1-2-3

W. P. A., photo
Five Boroughs Project
